{
  "texts": [
    "The x-axis shows pfSense and Snort, generating logs that are processed by the four SIEM systems while the y-axis shows the EPS achieved by each SIEM system.",
    "As depicted in the graph, Wazuh has the highest EPS of around 14K, 10K for pfSense, Snort respectively.",
    "The next is OSSIM with EPS of 9.5K, 9.1K, 0.89K and 0.91K respectively.",
    "Elastic Security is in 3rd place with EPS of 8.9K, 7.2K, 0.95K and 0.96K respectively.",
    "The last is SIE-Monster with EPS of 7.6K, 6.4K, 0.79K and 0.82K respectively."
  ]
}